Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, kdeconnect
Description: Indicator for KDE Connect
 KDE Connect is tool to integrate the KDE Plasma Workspace with your smartphones and
 similar devices.
 this indicator is aiming to bring those integration on any system using libappindicator
